<p style="border:solid black; padding: 1em"><b>Sorry, currently this playground does not work properly, because Spotify requires full authentication when
    somebody requests any data of artists or albums. Details about
        this on <a href="https://developer.spotify.com/news-stories/2017/01/27/removing-unauthenticated-calls-to-the-web-api/">Spotify developer news</a>
        <br/><br/>
        Follow <a href="https://github.com/lowsky/spotify-graphql-server/issues/42">issue #42 for updates</a></b></p>

<div class="grey">

<h2 class="grey">Try these predefined queries in graphiql playground:</h2>

<p>Start a query for <br>
    <a href='./graphql?query=%7B%0A%20%20queryArtists(byName%3A%22Red%20Hot%20Chili%20Peppers%22)%20%7B%0A%20%20%20%20name%0A%20%20%20%20id%0A%20%20%20%20image%0A%20%20%7D%0A%7D%0A'>
